ProductShortDescription: So fast. So agile. So stable. So comfortable. So simple. Just hop on the light and durable chromoly frame, settle your tush into the comfy saddle, place your feet on the pedals and let the single speed drivetrain do all the work for you.

  • Higher-range 24-speed drivetrain med TruVativ cranks giver dig mulighed for at holde øje med hurtigere gruppeture
  • Shimano RapidFire Plus shifters giver skarpere skift og et mere sikkert greb
  • K2 Fitness Road sadel med gelpolstring, tredobbelt tæthedsgreb og stående håndtag holder dig komfortabel, alle kører lange
  • Tektro RX-1 line-pull bremser kombinerer maksimal stopkraft med minimal indsats
  • Kenda Kwick Roller Sport dæk med halvglat center mønster mønster til plys, hurtigrulle præstationer
  • Bagstativmonteringer giver dig mulighed for at tilføje et stativ, når du skal transportere ekstra gear

ProductShortDescription: Road Bike Action, March/April 2008 - THE VERDICT - “Sometimes a good idea is only that, but with the Prologue, a good idea created a nice bike for not just the true beginner, but for someone who wants to put a few seasons on a worthy steed and save enough money to travel to enter and travel to events. This isn’t a low-level road bike frame with aerobars slapped on - it’s designed, built and outfitted with a purpose.
ProductLongDescription:
• N’Litened Gold Label aluminum aero frame with TT geometry puts you in the perfect position for lightweight speed
  • Black Label Carbon Pro Aero fork absorbs road vibration and delivers a smooth ride
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo cranks supply sleek, stiff pedaling power for the hills and the flats
  • Shimano 105/Tiagra derailleurs and bar end shifters put snappy shifting action within easy reach
  • Aerodynamic handlebar, stem and seatpost give you a wind-cheating advantage
  • Selle San Marco Ponza Trilon saddle keeps you comfortable when you’re down in the drops
  • Tektro RX-40 brakes provide maximum stopping power in any condition
  • Jalco/Formula wheels with Schwalbe Lugano tires pave the way to a fast finish

ProductShortDescription: Road Bike Action, marts / april 2008 - THE VERDICT - "Sommetider er det kun en god idé, men med Prologue har en god ide skabt en dejlig cykel for ikke kun den sande begynder, men for en person, der ønsker at sætte et par årstider på en værdig steed og spar nok penge til at rejse for at komme ind og rejse til arrangementer. Dette er ikke en cykelramme på lavt niveau med aerobarer slået på - den er designet, bygget og udstyret med et formål. Der er et par firmaer derude, der har en Tri / TT-cykel, men få er tilgængelige med out-of-the-box bar-end shifting, et aero-specifikt design og en solid komponentpakke til $ 999. Godt arbejde, Schwinn. "
ProductLongDescription:
• N'Litened Gold Label aluminium aero ramme med TT geometri sætter dig i den perfekte position til letvægts hastighed
  • Black Label Carbon Pro Aero gaffel absorberer vejvibrationer og giver en glidende tur
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo cranks leverer slank, stiv pedal effekt til bakkerne og lejlighederne
  • Shimano 105 / Tiagra derailleurs og bar end shifters sætter snappy skiftende handling inden for rækkevidde
  • Aerodynamisk håndtag, stængel og sædepost giver dig en vindende snyd fordel
  • Selle San Marco Ponza Trilon sadlen holder dig behagelig, når du er i dråberne
  • Tektro RX-40 bremser giver maksimal stopkraft i enhver tilstand
  • Jalco / Formula hjul med Schwalbe Lugano dæk bane vejen til en hurtig finish

ProductName: GT GTR Series Three Road Bike
ProductShortDescription: Race along the flats and smash any hill in your path with this super-fast bike! Shimano Tiagra compact cranks and 12/25T 9-speed cassette give you plenty of low gears for chewing up mountains without compromising speed when the road levels out.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hydroformed Kinesis aluminum frame is super-lightweight and responsive on the road
  • Kinesis carbon fork absorbs vibrations for a smooth, buttery ride
  • Shimano Tiagra/Sora 18-speed drivetrain with compact cranks and S.T.I. shifters offer plenty of quick, easy and efficient gearing options for the climbs
  • GT Road saddle adds cushioning to your backside
  • Tektro forged dual pivot brakes deliver maximum stopping power with minimal effort
  • Vittoria Zaffiro tires provide flexible comfort and puncture resistance
  • Semi-aero Alex D22 rims coupled with Formula/Shimano hubs give you added control and cornering confidence when the pace picks up

ProductName: GT GTR Series Three Road Bike
ProductShortDescription: Race langs lejlighederne og smad alle bakker i din vej med denne super-hurtige cykel! Shimano Tiagra kompakte kranker og 12 / 25T 9-trins kassette giver dig masser af lave gear til at tygge op i bjergene uden at gå på kompromis med hastigheden, når vejen går ud.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hydroformet Kinesis aluminiumsramme er super-let og lydhør på vejen
  • Kinesis carbon gaffel absorberer vibrationer for en glat, buttery ride
  • Shimano Tiagra / Sora 18-trins drivetrain med kompakte cranks og S.T.I. shifters tilbyder masser af hurtige, nemme og effektive gearing muligheder for klatring
  • GT Road sadel tilføjer pude til din bagside
  • Tektro smedede dobbelt drejebremser giver maksimal stopkraft med minimal indsats
  • Vittoria Zaffiro dæk giver fleksibel komfort og punkteringsmodstand
  • Semi-aero Alex D22 fælge kombineret med Formula / Shimano hubs giver dig ekstra kontrol og sving selvtillid, når tempoet henter

ProductShortDescription: Clean, smooth and wonderfully comfortable, the Legato is a ride that’s hard to forget. It blends together the speed of a road bike with the comfort and upright positioning of a hybrid, to give you a ride that’s fun, fast AND friendly to your body.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hydroformed Kinesis aluminum frame and fork is super-lightweight and responsive on the road
  • Women’s Specific Geometry is shaped with a taller head tube, steeper seat tube angle and shorter top tube length for a customized fit
  • Shimano 18-speed drivetrain with FSA Omega Compact cranks offer plenty of easy and efficient gearing options for the climbs
  • Flat handlebars with Rapid Fire shifters makes changing shifting easy and comfortable
  • Selle San Marco Women’s Ischia and dual density gel grips add comfort
  • Vittoria Zaffiro tires provide flexible comfort and puncture resistance
  • Tektro Forged Mini V-brakes deliver strong, easy braking

ProductShortDescription: Ren, glat og vidunderligt behagelig, Legato er en tur, der er svært at glemme. Det kombinerer hastigheden på en road cykel med komfort og opret positionering af en hybrid, for at give dig en tur, der er sjovt, hurtigt og venligt til din krop.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hydroformet Kinesis aluminiumsramme og gaffel er superlette og lydhøre på vejen
  • Kvindernes specifikke geometri er formet med et højere hovedrør, stejlere sæderørsvinkel og kortere rørlange for en tilpasset pasform
  • Shimano 18-speed drivetrain med FSA Omega Compact cranks tilbyder masser af nemme og effektive gearingsmuligheder til klatringerne
  • Flad håndtag med Rapid Fire shifters gør skiftende skift nemt og behageligt
  • Selle San Marco Women's Ischia og dual density gelhåndtag giver komfort
  • Vittoria Zaffiro dæk giver fleksibel komfort og punkteringsmodstand
  • Tektro Smedede Mini V-bremser giver stærk, nem bremsning

ProductShortDescription: Do you like the fast rolling, efficient nature of a good road bike but prefer the flatbar fit and comfort of a mountain bike? Thanks to the Roma, now you can have the best of both worlds!
ProductLongDescription:
• 7005 butted aluminum frame gives you a lightweight and stiff ride with high-performance characteristics
  • Shimano/SRAM drivetrain provides smooth and precise shifting action
  • TruVativ IF Road triple cranks deliver a powerful pedal stroke through hilly sections
  • Forté Flatbar handlebar and saddle keep you comfortably upright and eliminate extra weight on your hands, shoulders and back
  • Tektro RX-1 linear-pull brakes combine maximum stopping power with minimal effort
  • Kenda Kwest tires roll fast and smooth while the tread design offers excellent traction in wet or dry conditions
  • Seatpost mounted rear rack holds all your extra gear
  • Handlebar bell lets everyone know you’re comin’ around the bend

ProductShortDescription: Kan du lide den hurtige rullende, effektive karakter af en god vejcykel, men foretrækker flatbar pasform og komfort på en mountainbike? Takket være romaerne kan du nu få det bedste fra begge verdener!
ProductLongDescription:
• 7005 rammet aluminiumsramme giver dig en let og stiv ride med højtydende egenskaber
  • Shimano / SRAM drivetrain giver en jævn og præcis skiftende handling
  • TruVativ IF Road triple cranks leverer et kraftigt pedal slag gennem kuperede sektioner
  • Forté Flatbar styret og sadlen holder dig komfortabelt opret og eliminerer ekstra vægt på dine hænder, skuldre og ryg
  • Tektro RX-1 line-pull bremser kombinerer maksimal stopkraft med minimal indsats
  • Kenda Kwest dæk ruller hurtigt og glat, mens slidbanet design giver fremragende trækkraft i våde eller tørre forhold
  • Seatpostmonteret bagstativ holder alt dit ekstra gear
  • Håndtagsklokke lader alle vide, at du er kommet rundt om bøjningen

ProductShortDescription: For those “no work, all play” days, the Ocho arrives at your door ready for a few hours of frolic and fun before going on your way! Lightweight comfort geometry features the stylish Shimano Alfine drivetrain and an internal 8-speed hub to keep you looking and cycling in such relaxed style, that people will start wondering what your magic potion is. And when they ask, just pull out your coffee thermos, lean back on the saddle, look at your ride, give them a great big smile and then tell them…
ProductLongDescription:
• Lightweight aluminum frame with comfort geometry makes cycling a breeze
  • Sporty, Shimano Alfine drivetrain gives you extra comfort, control and sporty style while riding
  • Internal 8-speed hub combines clean looks with a wide range of gear options
  • Hollowtech II 2-piece cranks put pedaling power, acceleration and speed right at your feet
  • Aluminum flatbar with Bio-Tuned ergo bar ends and dual density saddle offer comfortable, more upright positioning
  • Continental City Contact tires provide excellent protection without compromising speed or weight
  • Hydraulic disc brakes deliver rapid and controlled stopping power in any condition
  • Alex rims with Shimano Center-Lock hubs offer the durable stability you need for longer rides
  • Stainless steel coffee thermos with cage makes your morning commute a little more tasty

ProductShortDescription: For de "ingen arbejde, alle spil" dage, kommer Ocho til din dør klar til et par timers frolic og sjov, før du går på vej! Letvægtskomfort geometri er udstyret med den stilfulde Shimano Alfine-drivetrain og et internt 8-trins hub, der holder dig til at kigge og cykle i en sådan afslappet stil, at folk vil begynde at spekulere på, hvad din magiske potion er. Og når de spørger, skal du bare trække din kaffe termos, læne dig tilbage på sadlen, se på din tur, give dem et stort stort smil og fortæl dem så ...
ProductLongDescription:
• Let aluminiumsramme med komfortgeometri gør cykling til en brise
  • Sporty, Shimano Alfine drivetrain giver dig ekstra komfort, kontrol og sporty stil under ridning
  • Intern 8-trins hub kombinerer rent udseende med en lang række gearindstillinger
  • Hollowtech II 2-delt krumtap sætte pedalkraft, acceleration og hastighed lige ved dine fødder
  • Aluminium flatbar med Bio-Tuned ergo bar ender og dual density sadle tilbyder behagelig, mere opretstående positionering
  • Kontinentaldæk fra Continental City giver fremragende beskyttelse uden at gå på kompromis med hastighed eller vægt
  • Hydrauliske skivebremser leverer hurtig og styret stopkraft i enhver tilstand
  • Alex fælge med Shimano Center-Lock hubs tilbyder den holdbare stabilitet, du har brug for til længere rides
  • Rustfrit stål kaffe termos med bur gør din morgen pendle lidt mere velsmagende

ProductName: GT GTR Type CX Road Bike
ProductShortDescription: If you’re a weekend warrior or a hard-riding enthusiast looking for a CX bike that’s built to withstand some serious abuse, then this is your ride! GT’s Cyclocross frame design offers exceptional strength and fatigue resistance while the SRAM 20-speed drivetrain will have you cycling in the dirt, on the road, up steep inclines and down vertical descents with incredible speed.
ProductLongDescription:
• GT Cyclocross frame design with butted Kinesis Kinesium aluminum is stronger than 6061 or 7005 series and delivers a ride that’s lightweight, rigid and exceptionally stable
  • Easton EC70 XC fork with carbon blades offers the perfect blend of strength and stiffness for CX riding
  • SRAM Rival drivetrain is built for serious and competitive riders who hammer on their gear day in and day out and demand technology that’s durable and long-lasting
  • TruVativ Rouleur cranks provide reliable speed and a powerful pedal stroke
  • SRAM Rival DoubleTap controls utilize a single lever for shifting and a dedicated lever for braking to provide smooth up and downshifting in ONE motion
  • Easton EA70 handlebars, stem and seatpost deliver core-level strength, style and performance
  • Tektro 720 Cantilever brakes with a retro design give you excellent and stylish stopping power
  • Easton Vista SL wheelset with Panaracer Cinder X tires offer incredible speed, grip and performance in wet or dry conditions

ProductName: GT GTR Type CX Road Bike
ProductShortDescription: Hvis du er en weekendkæmper eller en ridende entusiast på udkig efter en CX-cykel, der er bygget til at modstå noget alvorligt misbrug, så er det din tur! GT's Cyclocross-rammeprofil giver ekstraordinær styrke og træthedsresistens, mens SRAM 20-speed-drivkørslen får dig til at cykle i snavs, på vejen, op ad stejle skråninger og ned ad vertikale nedstigninger med utrolig fart.
ProductLongDescription:
• GT Cyclocross ramme design med stødt Kinesis Kinesium aluminium er stærkere end 6061 eller 7005 serien og leverer en tur, der er let, stiv og exceptionelt stabil
  • Easton EC70 XC gaffel med carbonblad giver den perfekte blanding af styrke og stivhed til CX-ridning
  • SRAM Rival drivkørsel er bygget til seriøse og konkurrencedygtige ryttere, der hammer på deres gear dag ind og dag ud og kræver teknologi, der er holdbar og langvarig
  • TruVativ Rouleur cranks giver pålidelig fart og en kraftig pedal slagtilfælde
  • SRAM Rival DoubleTap-betjeninger bruger en enkelt håndtag til skift og en dedikeret håndtag til bremsning for at give glat op og nedskiftning i ONE motion
  • Easton EA70 håndtag, stamme og sædepost leverer styrke, stil og ydeevne på kerneniveau
  • Tektro 720 Cantilever bremser med retro design giver dig fremragende og stilfuld stopkraft
  • Easton Vista SL hjulsæt med Panaracer Cinder X dæk tilbyder utrolig hastighed, greb og ydeevne under våde eller tørre forhold

ProductShortDescription: GT’s new radical and high performing GTR Pro Rival road bike pushes the tech envelope with cutting-edge looks and state of the art componentry. With a forced-optimized carbon chassis and SRAM Rival gruppo, this 17lb. thoroughbred is sure to place at the top of its class!
ProductLongDescription:
• GTR carbon monocoque frame with Ritchey Pro Carbon fork delivers a smooth, lightweight and vibration damping ride
  • Full SRAM Rival drivetrain is built for serious and competitive riders who hammer on their gear day in and day out and demand technology that’s durable and long-lasting
  • Ritchey aluminum handlebar and stem with carbon seatpost provide lightweight stiffness and have been perfectly positioned for race-ready performance
  • SRAM Rival DoubleTap controls utilize a single lever for shifting and a dedicated lever for braking to provide smooth up and downshifting in ONE motion
  • SRAM Rival dual pivot brakes provide excellent stopping power in any condition and enhance progressive feel
  • Shimano 105 wheelset paired with Vittoria Rubino Pro tires give you a high level of control, response and lateral rigidity for high mileage training

ProductShortDescription: GT's nye radikale og højtydende GTR Pro Rival road cykel skubber tech-konvolutten med banebrydende udseende og state of the art componentry. Med et tvunget optimeret carbon chassis og SRAM Rival gruppo, denne 17lb. thoroughbred er sikker på at placere i toppen af sin klasse!
ProductLongDescription:
• GTR carbon monocoque ramme med Ritchey Pro Carbon gaffel giver en glat, letvægts- og vibrationsdæmpningstur
  • Fuld SRAM Rival drivetrain er bygget til seriøse og konkurrencedygtige ryttere, som hammer på deres gear dag ind og dag ud og kræver teknologi, der er holdbar og langvarig
  • Ritchey aluminiumshåndtag og stængel med carbon sædepost giver let stivhed og er perfekt placeret til race-klar præstation
  • SRAM Rival DoubleTap-betjeninger bruger en enkelt håndtag til skift og en dedikeret håndtag til bremsning for at give glat op og nedskiftning i ONE motion
  • SRAM Rival dobbelt drejebremser giver fremragende stopkraft i enhver tilstand og forbedrer progressiv følelse
  • Shimano 105 hjulsæt parret med Vittoria Rubino Pro dæk giver dig et højt niveau af kontrol, respons og lateral stivhed til højkørsel

ProductShortDescription: A rack designed for mounting a set of pannier bags on bikes without threaded eyelets or full suspension bikes.
ProductLongDescription:
• Heat-treated 6000 series aluminum with powdercoat finish is tough enough to handle your gear
  • Easily attaches to the seatpost of most bikes using a forged 4-bolt clamp
  • Accepts panniers, rack trunks, baskets or bags
  • Curved for seat clearance
  • 25lb. load capacity

ProductShortDescription: Et stativ designet til montering af et sæt pannierposer på cykler uden gevindforbindelser eller fuldophængscykler.
ProductLongDescription:
• Varmebehandlet 6000-serien aluminium med pulverlaken er hård nok til at håndtere dit gear
  • Fastgøres nemt til de fleste cyklers sædestolpe ved hjælp af en smedet 4-bolts klemme
  • Accepterer panniers, rack trunks, kurve eller poser
  • Bøjet til sædeklaration
  • 25lb. belastningskapacitet

ProductShortDescription: Perfect for bikes without dropout eyelets or dual-suspension bikes.
ProductLongDescription:
• Secures with four Allen bolts
  • Fits seatpost sizes 25.0-31.8mm
  • 20lb load capacity

ProductShortDescription: Perfekt til cykler uden dropout eyelets eller dual-suspension cykler.
ProductLongDescription:
• Sikrer med fire boltbolte
  • Passer til sædepoststørrelser 25.0-31.8mm
  • 20 lb lastkapacitet

ProductShortDescription: Attach this rack to any bike - full suspension bikes or road bikes without braze-ons.
ProductLongDescription:
• Quick release attaches securely to any 24-32mm seatpost
  • Tough welded aluminum construction
  • Includes shims to prevent scratches
  • 25lb. capacity

ProductShortDescription: Fastgør denne rack til enhver cykel - fuld suspension cykler eller roadcykler uden bølger.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hurtig udløsning fastgøres sikkert til en 24-32mm sædepost
  • Hård svejset aluminiumkonstruktion
  • Indeholder shims for at forhindre ridser
  • 25lb. kapacitet

ProductShortDescription: A-tisket, A-tasket, A-convenient lift-off basket!
ProductLongDescription:
• Just place the mounting holder over your handlebar, insert the basket and Walla - you’ve got a place to stash all your extra items!
  • Basket easily lifts off the holder
  • Features a handle for carrying convenience
  • Built tough with a rust resistant finish for years of durable use
  • Easy, tool-free installation
  • Compatible with most handlebars
  • Not compatible with racing-style handlebars

ProductShortDescription: A-tisket, A-opgave, A-bekvem lift-off kurv!
ProductLongDescription:
• Placer kun monteringsholderen over dit håndtag, indsæt kurven og Walla - du har et sted at stash alle dine ekstra varer!
  • Kurven løfter let op af holderen
  • Har et håndtag til bærbar bekvemmelighed
  • Bygget hård med rustbeskyttende finish i mange års varig brug
  • Nem, værktøjsfrit installation
  • Kompatibel med de fleste styrestænger
  • Ikke kompatibel med racing-stil håndtag

ProductShortDescription: This rack is designed to take the abuse of the trail and heavy touring.
ProductLongDescription:
• Made from tough, lightweight aluminum, this rack is designed to work with the Topeak MTX Trunk Bag dX, see item #20-5215
  • Just slide it on, clip it in place and you're ready to hit the trail with all your cargo securely in place
  • Quick release seatpost mount
  • 20lb. capacity

ProductShortDescription: Denne rack er designet til at tage misbrug af sporet og tunge touring.
ProductLongDescription:
• Denne rack er lavet af hård, let aluminium og er designet til at fungere sammen med Topeak MTX Trunk Bag dX, se varen # 20-5215
  • Bare skub det på, klipp det på plads, og du er klar til at slå trailet med hele din last sikkert på plads
  • Hurtiglås sædepost mount
  • 20lb. kapacitet

ProductShortDescription: Perfect for a trip to the market or a lazy afternoon ride with your favorite pet, this euro-style basket puts simplicity back into your summer days!
ProductLongDescription:
• Hand woven, natural willow is perfectly sized to hold a bag of groceries
  • Three leather straps with buckles easily attach to your handlebar and stem
  • Want to carry your basket? Just unfasten it
  • Compatible with most handlebars

ProductShortDescription: Perfekt til en tur til markedet eller en doven eftermiddagstur med dit yndlingsdyr, denne kurv i euro-stil sætter enkelhed tilbage i dine sommerdage!
ProductLongDescription:
• Håndvævede, naturlige pil er perfekt dimensioneret til at holde en taske med dagligvarer
  • Tre læderremme med spænder kan nemt fastgøres til styret og stammen
  • Vil du bære din kurv? Bare løs det
  • Kompatibel med de fleste styrestænger

ProductShortDescription: For those who are serious about the road, the XRL Team frame and fork is in a class of its own when it comes to race-ready performance.
ProductLongDescription:
• Lightweight 7005 butted, aluminum tubeset is intricately shaped and manipulated for speed with its carbon S-bend stays and teardrop-shaped down tube and top tube
  • Uses the same race-inspired geometry found the 2007 Scattante R-660 Double Road Bike (see item #30-0034) for an excellent balance of predictable handling
  • Carbon fiber fork with aluminum steerer dampen vibrations for a smooth riding experience
  • Small details were not overlooked: look close and you’ll find a replaceable dropout, an integrated headset, pro paint and fast graphics
  • Comes complete with a carbon/aluminum fork, integrated headset and CNC machined seat post collar

ProductShortDescription: For dem der er seriøse over vejen er XRL-teamets ramme og gaffel i en klasse, når det kommer til race-klar præstation.
ProductLongDescription:
• Letvægts 7005 stødt aluminiumsrør er indviklet formet og manipuleret til hastighed med dets carbon S-bøjninger og tårnformet nedrør og toprør
  • Bruger den samme race-inspirerede geometri fundet 2007 Scattante R-660 Double Road Bike (se vare nr. 30-0034) for en fremragende balance af forudsigelig håndtering
  • Kobberfibergaffel med aluminiumstyrer dæmper vibrationer for en glidende rideoplevelse
  • Små detaljer blev ikke overset: Se tæt på, og du finder et udskifteligt udfald, et integreret headset, pro-farvning og hurtig grafik
  • Leveres komplet med en carbon / aluminium gaffel, integreret headset og CNC-maskineret sædepostkrave

ProductShortDescription: Blackburn’s strongest rack is built for extended tours, off-road rides and long distance commutes. And it even holds a child seat for safe transport of your little one!
ProductLongDescription:
• Welded, oversized aluminum construction with a reinforced frame and powder coated finish delivers bombproof performance
  • 3/8” center strut stabilizes your load and maximizes strength
  • Accommodates panniers or a child seat
  • 40lb. capacity
  • Braze-on design
  • Fits most bikes
  • Mounting hardware included

ProductShortDescription: Blackburns stærkeste rack er bygget til udvidede ture, off-road-rides og lange afstande pendler. Og det rummer endda et barnestol til sikker transport af din lille!
ProductLongDescription:
• Svejset, overdimensioneret aluminiumkonstruktion med forstærket ramme og pulverlakeret finish giver bomuldssikker ydeevne
  • 3/8 "centerstiver stabiliserer din belastning og maksimerer styrken
  • Plads til panniers eller et barnesæde
  • 40 lb. kapacitet
  • Braze-on design
  • Passer til de fleste cykler
  • Monterings hardware inkluderet

ProductShortDescription: The same bike ridden by the 2016 China Olympic BMX Team!
ProductLongDescription:
• 6061 aluminum frame with chromoly fork delivers tough-as-nails performance while remaining exceptionally light and rigid
  • 3-piece tubular chromoly cranks with a 44T aluminum crank guarantee a light, stiff and durable ride
  • T.H.E. Dice saddle won’t get in your way when you’re racin’ or just showing off
  • Tektro 930 V-brakes offer excellent stopping power
  • Kenda Small Block tires with smaller knobs provide incredible grip and traction
  • Alienation PBR race rimes with 36H sealed aluminum hubs are perfect for jumping and racing
  • Protective T.H.E. padset and number plate are the perfect accessories for your next race

ProductShortDescription: Den samme cykel ridt af 2016 China Olympic BMX Team!
ProductLongDescription:
• 6061 aluminiumsramme med kromolygaffel leverer hård-som-negle ydeevne, mens den forbliver yderst let og stiv
  • 3-delt rørformede kromoly cranks med 44T aluminiumsvinkel garanterer en let, stiv og holdbar ride
  • DET. Dice sadel vil ikke komme i din vej, når du er racin 'eller bare vise sig
  • Tektro 930 V-bremser tilbyder fremragende stopkraft
  • Kenda Small Block dæk med mindre knapper giver utrolig greb og trækkraft
  • Forlængelse PBR race rimes med 36H forseglede aluminium hubs er perfekte til spring og racing
  • Beskyttende T.H.E. padset og nummerplade er det perfekte tilbehør til dit næste løb

ProductShortDescription: Now parents can hit the track with their kids on this 24” BMX bike!
ProductLongDescription:
• 6061 aluminum frame with chromoly fork delivers tough-as-nails performance while remaining exceptionally light and rigid
  • 3-piece tubular chromoly cranks guarantee a stiff and durable ride
  • T.H.E. Dice saddle won’t get in your way when you’re racin’ or just showing off
  • Tektro V-brakes offer excellent stopping power
  • Kenda Small Block tires with smaller knobs provide incredible grip and traction
  • Overbuilt Alex F303 rims with 36H aluminum hubs withstand all sorts of abuse
  • Protective T.H.E. padset and number plate are the perfect accessories for your next race

ProductShortDescription: Nu kan forældre slå sporet med deres børn på denne 24 "BMX cykel!
ProductLongDescription:
• 6061 aluminiumsramme med kromolygaffel leverer hård-som-negle ydeevne, mens den forbliver yderst let og stiv
  • 3-delt rørformede kromoly cranks garanterer en stiv og holdbar ride
  • DET. Dice sadel vil ikke komme i din vej, når du er racin 'eller bare vise sig

ProductShortDescription: If you head to the woods with the full knowledge that you’re not coming back out in the same shape that you left…then quite possibly, we have your perfect ride! This chromoly-loaded bike takes to the air with incredible ease yet is built tough to absorb those inevitable hard landings. And with 100mm of front suspension, Sun Ditch Witch rims, FSA cranks and SRAM componentry, this bike will have no problem surviving anything you throw its way…but the question is, will you?
ProductLongDescription:
• Heavy-duty chromoly frame provides extra strength for jumps on the trail

  • SRAM X.5 9-speed rear shifter and SRAM X.7 derailleur blend smooth shifting action with quick and precise performance

  • Sun Ditch Witch rims with Mongoose rear disc hubs are built to withstand those tough hits

ProductShortDescription: Hvis du leder til skoven med den fulde viden om, at du ikke kommer tilbage i samme form som du forlod ... så har vi muligvis din perfekte tur! Denne chromolybelastede cykel fører til luften med utroligt lethed, men er bygget hårdt for at absorbere de uundgåelige hårde landinger. Og med 100mm forophæng, Sun Ditch Witch fælge, FSA cranks og SRAM componentry, vil denne cykel ikke have noget problem at overleve alt, hvad du kaster sin vej ... men spørgsmålet er, vil du?
ProductLongDescription:

  • Marzocchi Dirt Jumper 2 gaffel tilbyder 100mm plys suspension for at absorbere de store hits
  • FSA Moto X cranks med PC bashguard er bygget hårde og stærke til alle dine freeride escapades
  • SRAM X.5 9-speed bagudskifter og SRAM X.7 derailleur blander glat skiftende handling med hurtig og præcis ydeevne

ProductShortDescription: Mongoose shaved some weight off of last year’s Teocali frame and still managed to add beefier pivots and bearings to the 5.7 inches of tried and true FreeDrive rear wheel suspension. With an Easton cockpit, a heavy dose of Shimano/SRAM components and tough WTB wheels, this sharply dressed bike is perfectly built for those all-mountain, all-day-in-the-saddle rides.

  • Fox Float RP/2 rear shock with two-piston ProPedal allows on-the-fly tuning for changing terrain while smoothing out the rough spots
  • SRAM X.7 Impulse Triggers and X.9 rear derailleur provide incredibly smooth, precise indexing and control
  • Shimano Hollowtech II cranks put pedaling power, acceleration and speed right at your feet
  • Easton aluminum handlebars, stem and Mongoose seatpost deliver core-level strength, style and performance
  • Hayes Stroker Trail V6 hydraulic disc brakes guarantee rapid, controlled and perfectly modulated stopping power in any condition
  • WTB Speed Disc All Mountain rims with 20mm hubs and Kenda Nevegal tires are built to handle anything you can dish out on the trail

ProductShortDescription: Mongoose barberede en del vægt af sidste års Teocali-ramme og lykkedes stadig at tilføje beefier-pivoter og lejer til 5,7 inches af prøvet og sandt FreeDrive baghjulsophæng. Med en Easton-cockpit, en kraftig dosis Shimano / SRAM-komponenter og hårde WTB-hjul, er denne skarpt klædte cykel perfekt bygget til dem alle bjerg, hele dagen i sadel-rides.

ProductShortDescription: This bike will have you turning those “short afternoon rides” into “epic trail runs” thanks to its climb-friendly setup! GT’s patented Independent Drivetrain system eliminates pedal feedback, so you can go longer and harder. Add on the bump-absorbing, dual suspension from Rock Shox and Fox, a Shimano 27-speed drivetrain, disc wheels and Kenda tires that grip like a vice, and you’ll start to wonder how you ever rode less than four hours a day!

ProductShortDescription: So your little angel suddenly became a wildcat overnight? He’ll soon figure out that the training wheels are removable which means you’ll probably find them somewhere in your driveway. Colorful handlebar streamers and tiger graphics will have him ridin’ on the wild side.

Og med Shimano's præcision 105-drivkørslen, den ekstra klatstyrke af FSA-carbon-cranks og et letvægtshjulsæt til toppen af det, er der ikke noget, hvor mange vinder denne tur kommer til at bringe hjem!

ProductShortDescription: Lad ikke denne sadel se glat ser distrahere dig. Letvægts og spec'd at imponere, denne pro-level sadel vil forbløffe dig med sin utrolige komfort!

• 30% carbon komposit skal er anatomisk designet til en perfekt pasform, mens du tilbyder en premium, vibrationsdæmpningstur
  • Selle Italiens specielle udskæring begynder på bagsiden af sadlen, hvilket gør det muligt for højre og venstre side at bevæge sig uafhængigt af hinanden - dette efterligner den naturlige pedalbevægelse, samtidig med at man får mere bøjning på sadlen og omkring sitbenene
  • Silikongelindsatser med differentieret tykkelse er strategisk placeret rundt om den anatomiske udskæring for at forbedre komforten og aflaste trykket i det frontale bløde vævsområde
  • Perfekt Fit padding klæber til din krop for yderligere support
  • Åndbar, fuldkornet læderdæksel
  • Vanox rørformede skinner med carbonindpakning giver jævn og letvægt

ProductShortDescription: If you want baptism by air, here’s your ride. Not only does this bike clear big jumps with ease, its tough, chromoly frame feels nearly weightless when you’re off the ground! Add on 100mm of front suspension to cushion the drops and 3-piece cranks for that sweet barspin, and you’ve got yourself a ride that can tackle anything on the ground or in the air.
ProductLongDescription:
• Lightweight aluminum frame with carbon fork offers a stiff and efficient ride with less vibration
  • Shimano 105 Triple drivetrain gives you high performance, reliable speed and conquers every hill in your path
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo cranks deliver sleek, stiff pedaling power for the hills and the flats
  • Aluminum handlebar, seatpost and stem supply core-level strength, style and performance
  • Kenda tires keep you moving along at high speeds while remaining exceptionally quiet against the pavement
  • Alex ALX 270 wheelset cuts through the wind with bladed spokes, aero rims and smooth rolling hubs
  • Tektro R530 dual pivot calipers deliver strong, progressive stopping power and good modulation

ProductShortDescription: Hvis du vil have dåb med fly, her er din tur. Ikke alene gør denne cykel klart store spring med lethed, den hårde chromoliske ramme føles næsten vægtløs, når du er ude af jorden! Tilføj på 100mm forhjulsophæng for at dæmpe dråberne og 3-delede vinkler til den søde spids, og du har selv en tur, der kan tackle alt på jorden eller i luften.
ProductLongDescription:
• Letvægts aluminiumramme med carbongaffel giver en stiv og effektiv ride med mindre vibrationer
  • Shimano 105 Triple drivetrain giver dig høj ydeevne, pålidelig fart og erobrer hver bakke i din vej
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo cranks leverer slank, stiv pedal effekt til bakkerne og lejlighederne
  • Aluminium håndtag, sædepost og stamforsyning kerneniveau styrke, stil og ydeevne
  • Kenda-dæk holder dig i bevægelse ved høje hastigheder, mens du forbliver usædvanligt stille mod fortovet
  • Alex ALX 270 hjulsæt skærer gennem vinden med bladede eger, aero felger og glatte rullende nav
  • Tektro R530 dual pivot calipers leverer stærk, progressiv stopkraft og god modulering

ProductShortDescription: Named after the most extreme climb in the Giro d’Italia, the Zoncolan gives you the right amount of ergonomic comfort for tackling those vertical ascents!
ProductLongDescription:
• San Marco’s Gelaround system adopts a polyurethane race-gel insert at the sit-bones and along the Arrowhead cut-out section to relieve pressure on blood vessels and urogenetial nerves - what you get is improved comfort without the extra weight
  • Carbon reinforced, nylon shell provides lightweight flexibility
  • Durable leather cover offers long-lasting performance
  • Titanium rails guarantee a smooth and light riding experience

ProductShortDescription: Navngivet efter den mest ekstreme klatre i Giro d'Italia giver Zoncolan dig den rigtige mængde ergonomisk komfort til at tackle de lodrette stigninger!
ProductLongDescription:
• San Marco's Gelaround-system vedtager en polyurethan race-gel indsats ved sidebenene og langs pilhovedudskæringssektionen for at lette trykket på blodkar og urogenetiale nerver - hvad du får, er bedre komfort uden ekstra vægt
  • Kulforstærket nylon skal giver letvægts fleksibilitet
  • Holdbart læder cover giver lang levetid
  • Titanium skinner garanterer en glat og let rideoplevelse

ProductShortDescription: Your favorite downhill chute might be the closest you’ll ever get to Paris fashion show runway. But we think everyone deserves to take a spin on the catwalk…or rather…on the trail. And that’s exactly why we decided to stock the Crank Brothers 5050 XX pedal. With its hard-hitting, durability; sealed bearing design and customizable plates and pins, you’ll be well on your way to some show-stopping style and performance on your next dirt-laden adventure!
ProductLongDescription:
• Removable and replaceable colored plates and 10mm set screws let you fully customize the look of your pedals
  • Aluminum body and plates with an oversized chromoly steel spindle are built tough to withstand heavy loads
  • Wide, 2-sided pedal surface offers excellent stability
  • Low profile design delivers a more powerful and efficient pedal stroke
  • Sealed cartridge bearing system is easy to maintain

ProductShortDescription: Din yndlingsbakke kan være den nærmeste, du nogensinde kommer til Paris modeshow. Men vi tror, at alle fortjener at tage et spin på catwalken ... eller rettere ... på sporet. Og det er netop derfor, vi besluttede at lagre Crank Brothers 5050 XX pedal. Med dens hårde rammer, holdbarhed; forseglet leje design og brugerdefinerbare plader og stifter, vil du være godt på vej til nogle show-stop stil og ydeevne på dit næste snavsbelastede eventyr!
ProductLongDescription:
• Aftagelige og udskiftelige farvede plader og 10 mm sætskruer giver dig mulighed for fuldt ud at tilpasse udseendet på dine pedaler
  • Aluminium krop og plader med en overdimensioneret chromoly stål spindel er bygget hårdt for at modstå tunge belastninger
  • Bred, 2-sidet pedaloverflade giver fremragende stabilitet
  • Lavprofildesign giver et mere kraftfuldt og effektivt pedalslag
  • Forseglet patronlagersystem er let at vedligeholde

ProductShortDescription: A high that’ll last as long as you ride! The Acid 2 pedal fills the gap between the cross-country Candy and the downhill Mallet to give you the perfect fix for enduro and gravity racing. Now designed with magnesium and carbon for a nearly “weightless” cycling experience!
ProductLongDescription:
• Utilizes the same proven retention system from the infamous Eggbeater pedal with a larger, more robust platform design for greater stability and increased power transfer
  • Magnesium/carbon fiber body with chromoly steel spindle and stamped steel wings give you an exceptionally lightweight and vibration damping ride while maintaining strength for technical descents and hard landings
  • 2-sided pedal surface offers firm support for your foot over rough terrain
  • 4-sided entry gives you quick, no-hassle engagement and release while remaining impervious to dirt and mud

ProductShortDescription: En høj, der holder så længe du kører! Acid 2-pedalen fylder afstanden mellem cross-country candy og downhill Mallet for at give dig den perfekte løsning til enduro og gravity racing. Nu designet med magnesium og kulstof til en næsten "vægtløs" cykeloplevelse!
ProductLongDescription:
• Udnytter det samme beviste tilbageholdelsessystem fra den berygtede Eggbeater-pedal med et større og mere robust platformdesign for større stabilitet og øget overførsel af strøm
  • Magnesium / karbonfiberkrop med chromoly stålspindel og stemplet stålvinger giver dig en usædvanlig letvægts- og vibrationsdæmpning, samtidig med at du styrker for tekniske nedstigninger og hårde landinger
  • 2-sidet pedaloverflade giver solid støtte til din fod over hårdt terræn
  • 4-sidet indgang giver dig hurtig, ubesværet indgreb og frigivelse, mens du stadig er uigennemtrængelig for snavs og mudder

ProductShortDescription: The original 4-sided pedal for the budget minded mountain or road rider.
ProductLongDescription:
• All-access design improves mud shedding while providing quick ‘n easy “no look” engagement and release
  • Stainless steel body and spring with chromoly spindle add durable strength and stability without a weight penalty
  • Low profile design delivers a more powerful and efficient pedal stroke
  • 6° of knee-saving float with a choice of a 15 or 20° release angle gives you a customized fit for the trail

ProductShortDescription: Den oprindelige 4-sidede pedal til budgetbegrænset bjerg- eller vejrør.
ProductLongDescription:
• Alt-adgangsdesign forbedrer mudslibningen, samtidig med at du hurtigt og nemt får det i kontakt og frigivelse
  • Rustfrit stål krop og forår med chromoly spindel tilføjer holdbar styrke og stabilitet uden en vægtstraf
  • Lavprofildesign giver et mere kraftfuldt og effektivt pedalslag
  • 6 ° af knæbesparende float med et valg af 15 eller 20 ° frigivelsesvinkel giver dig en tilpasset pasform til stien

ProductShortDescription: All of our wheels are hand-finished by our professional wheel builders.
ProductLongDescription:
• All of our wheels are hand-finished by our professional wheel builders.
  • Training or racing with performance you can count on
  • SUP-welded hard-anodized rims with double-eyelets for added strength
  • UB-machined braking surface for durability and sure stopping power
  • 8-9-10 speed Shimano Compatible

ProductShortDescription: Alle vores hjul er håndlavede af vores professionelle hjulbyggere.
ProductLongDescription:
• Alle vores hjul er håndlavede af vores professionelle hjulbyggere.
  • Træning eller racing med ydeevne, du kan stole på

ProductShortDescription: If climbing, sprinting and race-winning performance are your goals, then these are your weapons of choice!

  • Gen4 machined rims deliver sure stopping power
  • Offset design of the rear rim adds balance and rigidity
  • 18 front and 24 rear Sapim double-butted, stainless steel spokes enhance durability and aerodynamics

ProductShortDescription: Hvis klatring, sprint og race-vindende præstationer er dine mål, så er disse dine valgfrie våben!
ProductLongDescription:

  • Gen4 maskinfælge leverer sikker stopkraft
  • Offset design af den bageste kant tilføjer balance og stivhed
  • 18 front og 24 bag Sapim dobbeltspidsede, rustfrie stål eger forbedrer holdbarhed og aerodynamik

  • Fore drilled spoke holes make this rim 4x more stiff and rigid to give you better power transmission
  • UB Control coating delivers smooth and powerful braking action
  • 18 (radial) stainless steel, straight pull, bladed spokes add durable strength with increased aerodynamics
  • Removable and adjustable, sealed cartridge bearings are easy to maintain

  • 18 (radiale) rustfrit stål, lige træk, bladede eger øger holdbar styrke med øget aerodynamik

ProductShortDescription: At only 190g, the Aspide Glamour is one of the lightest, padded saddles around. And since it’s built around a women’s specific design, you can also bet that its one of the most comfortable!
ProductLongDescription:
• Carbon fiber reinforced shell with differentiated thickness provides lightweight flexibility, absorbs vibrations and is ergonomically designed to give you premium comfort and performance
  • Lorica cover and minimal padding offer breathable comfort for those day-long rides
  • Titanox rails deliver nearly “weightless” strength

ProductShortDescription: På kun 190g er Aspide Glamour en af de letteste polstrede sadler rundt. Og da det er bygget omkring et kvinders specifikke design, kan du også vædde på, at det er en af de mest komfortable!

ProductShortDescription: Gain the competitive edge for your next triathlon, time-trail or Sunday group ride on this feature-packed bike! Aluminum frame is designed to be comfortable enough for everyday riding, yet with the simple addition of aerobars, it easily transforms into a race-driven machine that performs on the sprints and in the climbs. Carbon fiber fork and seatpost smooth out the road ahead, high-end Shimano components put precision shifting within easy reach and the compact cranks give you everything you need to power up the climbs and sail down descents with confidence.
ProductLongDescription:
• 6061 double butted aluminum frame with carbon aero fork blades deliver a stiff, efficient ride with less road vibration
  • Shimano 105 components with Dura-Ace bar-end shift levers give you high performance, reliable speed and makes shifting quicker and easier than ever
  • FSA Energy Compact cranks with 11/23 cassette provide the right amount of gearing for the hills and flats
  • Removable Scattante aerobars let you customize your bike for comfort or racing
  • Tektro R570 dual pivot calipers offer strong, progressive stopping power and good modulation
  • Kenda tires keep you moving along at high speeds while remaining exceptionally quiet against the pavement
  • Alex ALX 320 Comp wheelset cuts through the wind with bladed spokes, aero rims and smooth rolling hubs

ProductShortDescription: Få konkurrencemæssig fordel for din næste triathlon, time-trail eller søndag gruppe tur på denne funktionelle cykel! Aluminiumsrammen er designet til at være komfortabel nok til hverdags ridning, men med den enkle tilføjelse af aerobarer, kan den let omdannes til en race-drevet maskine, der udfører på sprints og i klatrer. Kobberfibergaffel og sædepude glider ud af vejen foran, high-end Shimano-komponenter sætter præcisionskift inden for rækkevidde, og de kompakte krumtap giver dig alt hvad du behøver for at køre op ad klatrerne og sejle ned ned ad bakke.

  • Alex ALX 320 Comp hjulhjul skærer gennem vinden med bladede eger, aero fælge og glatte rullende nav

Just swing your leg over the Schwinn’s Classic Sport frame, seat yourself on the comfy sofa saddle, rest your hands naturally on the swept back handlebars and let the automatic shifting take care of the rest. Go ahead…relax…unwind…and roll on down the road to freedom.

Gå videre ... slappe af ... slappe af ... og rul ned ad vejen til frihed.

ProductShortDescription: So fast. So agile. So stable. So comfortable. So simple. Just hop on the light and durable chromoly frame, settle your tush into the comfy saddle, place your feet on the pedals and let the single speed drivetrain do all the work for you. Get going too fast? No problem. One pull the brake levers and the mechanical discs will slow you right down. And the tires? They’re ready to take you through all sorts of terrain. Trust us. You’re in for the ride of your life!
ProductLongDescription:
• GT Triple Triangle Single Speed chromoly frame and fork delivers a lightweight, durable and stiff ride
  • Single speed drivetrain with 18T rear cog is simple and uncomplicated to maintain
  • TruVativ cranks and bottom bracket give you an easy, yet powerful pedal stroke
  • Tektro Aquila mechanical disc brakes offer excellent stopping power in any condition
  • WTB SpeedDisc rims with ExiWolf tires are built to withstand all sorts of abuse

ProductShortDescription: Så hurtigt. Så agile. Så stabil. Så behagelig. Så simpelt. Bare hop på den lette og slidstærke chromoly ramme, sæt din tøs ind i den komfortable sæde, læg dine fødder på pedalerne, og lad enkeltdrevne drivkørsler gøre alt for dig. Går du for hurtigt? Intet problem. Man trækker bremsearmene, og de mekaniske skiver sætter dig langsomt ned. Og dækene? De er klar til at tage dig igennem alle slags terræn. Stol på os. Du er inde for dit livs tur!
ProductLongDescription:
• GT Triple Triangle Single Speed chromoly ramme og gaffel giver en let, holdbar og stiv ride
  • Single speed drivetrain med 18T bagkrog er enkel og ukompliceret at vedligeholde
  • TruVativ krumtap og bundbeslag giver dig en nem, men kraftig pedal slagtilfælde
  • Tektro Aquila mekaniske skivebremser tilbyder fremragende stopkraft i enhver tilstand
  • WTB SpeedDisc-fælge med ExiWolf-dæk er bygget til at modstå alle former for misbrug

ProductShortDescription: “If you’re looking for one bike that’ll tackle any sort of riding with enthusiasm, help you out when speed overruns skill and make sure you finish every ride grinning, we’d go for ‘Goose’s golden egg!” - Mountain Biking Magazine.
ProductLongDescription:
• Aluminum frame with FreeDrive design and slightly relaxed 69.5° head angle tackles loose-over-hard terrain with ease and responds quickly when its time to pick up speed
  • Rock Shox Tora 318 Air fork with 100mm of travel delivers smooth, predictable and reliable bump absorption over uneven terrain
  • Fox Float R gives you a wide range of compression control for incredibly accurate suspension tuning
  • Shimano XT drivetrain provides flawless shifting and performance on all types of terrain
  • Hayes Stroker Trail hydraulic disc brakes guarantee rapid and controlled stopping power in any condition
  • WTB Speed Disc XC rims with Shimano M525 hubs and Kenda Small Block Eight DCT tires offer the lightweight stability and traction you need on technical trails

ProductShortDescription: "Hvis du leder efter en cykel, der vil tackle enhver form for ridning med entusiasme, hjælpe dig ud, når hastigheden overskrider færdighed og sørg for at du er færdig med hver tur, grinning, ville vi gå til 'Goose's golden egg!' - Mountainbiking Magasin.

ProductShortDescription: If you want an elegant frame that’s reliable, easy to use and a joy to ride…look no further. Handmade by one of the world’s leading frame fabricators and designed using traditional geometry, premium specs, understated styling and horizontal dropouts, the Scattante SSR is the ideal choice for your next fixed-gear or single speed bicycle.
ProductLongDescription:
• Double butted chromoly steel frame delivers the optimum blend of stiffness, resiliency and overall low weight thanks to its smooth, clean welds and meticulous attention to detail
  • 1 1/8” head tube and rear facing, micro-adjustable, track-style dropouts allow the installation of any 120mm track hub so you can run a freewheel, fixed-gear drivetrain, flip-flop hubs or even internally geared or coaster brake hubs for a truly customized ride
  • Beautifully finished by an industry renowned paint shop to give you years of long lasting appearance and performance
  • Removable, die-cut logos have been applied over the paint
  • Complete decal set available separately: See item 90-0474
  • Don’t miss the Scattante SSR Fork; designed to work perfectly with this frame! See item #30-0903

ProductShortDescription: Hvis du vil have en elegant ramme, der er pålidelig, nem at bruge og en glæde at ride ... ser ikke længere ud. Scattante SSR er håndlavet af en af verdens førende rammefabrikanter og designet ved hjælp af traditionel geometri, premiumspecifikationer, undervurderet styling og vandrette udfald, og er det ideelle valg til din næste cykel med fast gear eller en enkelt cykel.
ProductLongDescription:
• Dobbeltstumpet chromoly stålramme giver den optimale blanding af stivhed, elasticitet og overordnet lav vægt takket være sine glatte, rene svejsninger og omhyggelig opmærksomhed på detaljer
  • 1 1/8 "hovedrør og bagudvendte, mikrojusterbare sporafbrydelser giver mulighed for installation af ethvert 120 mm spornav, så du kan køre en frihjul, fastgearkørsel, flip-flop hubs eller endda internt gearet eller coaster bremse hubber til en virkelig tilpasset tur
  • Smukt færdiggjort af en industriel kendt maleri for at give dig mange års varig udseende og ydeevne
  • Aftagelige, skårne logoer er påført over maling
  • Komplet dekal indstillet separat: Se punkt 90-0474
  • Gå ikke glip af Scattante SSR Fork; designet til at fungere perfekt med denne ramme! Se vare nr. 30-0903

  • Low profile design enhances pedaling power and efficiency

ProductName: Crank Brothers Quattro SL Road Pedal
ProductShortDescription: Hvis du er en Roadie, kan du bare ikke gå galt med denne premium pedal. Med sin lette design, slank profil, stort platformområde, justerbar klappositionering, ekstraordinær svingafstand og slankt look ... har du alt hvad du behøver for at pedalere som en proff!
ProductLongDescription:
• Udnytter det samme beviste tilbageholdelsessystem fra den berygtede Eggbeater-pedal med et større platformdesign for større stabilitet og øget overførsel af strøm
  • Kompositlegeme med rustfrit stålspindel og kulstofstålvinger giver let og holdbar ydeevne under alle omstændigheder
  • 2-sidet pedaloverflade giver et solidt fundament til din fod
  • 4-sidet indgang giver dig hurtig, ubesværet engagement og frigivelse
  • Juster klap positionen 15 eller 20 ° for at tilpasse din tur
  • Lavprofildesign forbedrer pedalkraft og effektivitet

ProductShortDescription: Looking for low-profile platforms? This is your pedal!
ProductLongDescription: • Durable alloy body accepts toe clips and straps

ProductShortDescription: Leder du efter lavprofil platforme? Dette er din pedal!

ProductName: Time ATAC XS Carbon MTB Pedal
ProductShortDescription: From the makers of the popular ATAC pedal comes the XS Carbon; a pedal with a smaller, lighter weight pedal body that performs better in any condition.
ProductLongDescription:
• Durable, lightweight carbon body, aluminum spring and chromoly axle create a solid connection to the cranks for total power transfer without a lot of added weight
  • New body profile facilitates faster entry and exit
  • Self-cleaning design sheds mud like no other
  • Sensor Elasticity Tuner allows you to personalize the sensation of float, giving you the choice of more or less resistance

ProductName: Time ATAC XS Carbon MTB Pedal
ProductShortDescription: Fra producenterne af den populære ATAC-pedal kommer XS Carbon; en pedal med en mindre, lettere vægt pedal krop, der udfører bedre i enhver tilstand.
ProductLongDescription:
• Slidstærk, letvægts karrosseri, aluminiumfjeder og chromolyaksel skaber en solid forbindelse til krumtapene til total kraftoverførsel uden meget ekstra vægt
  • Ny kropsprofil letter hurtigere indgang og udgang
  • Selvrensende design kaster ludder som ingen andre
  • Sensor Elasticitet Tuner giver dig mulighed for at personliggøre sensation af float, hvilket giver dig valget af mere eller mindre modstand

ProductShortDescription: This saddle was patterned after saddles on European commuter bikes – with the addition of a seamless cutaway.
ProductLongDescription:
• Ideal for commuter and hybrid bikes, this saddle was patterned after saddles on European commuter bikes
  • Contoured top with large cutaway is guaranteed to hit and miss in all the right places
  • Molded shock-absorbing elastomers create the effect of springs without any additional weight
  • Completely seamless a chafe-free ride
  • Long-lasting synthetic vinyl top is easy to maintain and will look new for years

ProductShortDescription: Denne sadel blev mønstret efter sadler på europæiske pendlercykler - med tilføjelse af en sømløs cutaway.
ProductLongDescription:
• Ideel til pendler og hybridcykler, denne sadel blev mønstret efter sadler på europæiske pendlercykler
  • Contoured top med stor cutaway er garanteret at ramme og savne på alle de rigtige steder
  • Støbte stødabsorberende elastomerer skaber effekten af fjedre uden yderligere vægt
  • Helt sømløs en chaffri tur
  • Langvarig syntetisk vinylplade er nem at vedligeholde og vil se nye i årevis

ProductShortDescription: Looking out your window on a cold winter morning usually produces a mental list of excuses as to why it would be better to stay in bed. So when we stumbled upon Cannondale’s Foul Weather tight, were surprised and delighted to find that it gave us many more reasons to head outside!
ProductLongDescription:
• Thermal HydroGrid fabric with 4-way stretch provides full water and windproof protection and unsurpassed breathability and flexibility; especially where your joints need the most mobility
  • Strategic seam construction follows your muscular-skeletal pattern for unparalleled fit, range of motion and comfort
  • Reflective accents offer 360° of visibility
  • Knee gussets further enhance flexibility
  • 10” leg zippers make it easy to get in and out of these tights
  • Drawstring waist gives you a custom fit
  • Internal stash pocket at hip will hold your cash, credit cards or keys

  • Full length zipper with draft flap blocks cold winds

  • D-Lux Mesh side panels deliver breathable comfort
  • Full shelf bra with extended support and plush elastic trim keeps those blossoming bosoms in line
  • T-back design adds the right amount of compression for activity
  • Gently flattering, non-elastic hem hits at just the right spot and is tailored specifically for women
  • Stash all your accessories in two rear pockets

ProductShortDescription: This  racer will having you weaving through tight turns, climbing up unrelenting hills, traveling over jagged terrain, blasting through mucky conditions.
ProductLongDescription:
• 7005 butted aluminum frame is lightweight, strong and rigid
  • Carbon bladed fork and seatpost dampens vibrations and offers a smooth, stiff ride
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo compact cranks give you a sleek and powerful pedal stroke for the flats and the climbs
  • Shimano 105 drivetrain combines reliable speed and high performance with incredible control and response
  • Carbon/aluminum seatpost with aluminum stem and handlebar guarantees core-level strength, style and performance
  • Kenda K-932 tires provide excellent traction and stability without compromising speed
  • Alex ALX 270 wheelset cuts through the wind with bladed spokes, aero rims and smooth rolling hubs
  • Tektro 992AG linear-pull brakes deliver perfectly modulated stopping power

ProductShortDescription: So fast. So agile. So stable. So comfortable. So simple.
ProductLongDescription:
• Aluminum hård hale frame is lightweight and delivers solid performance on the trail
  • 100mm of plush front suspension adds control and comfort in variable terrain
  • Shimano 24-speed drivetrain with 11/32T cassette gives you plenty of gearing options to choose from
  • EZ Fire trigger shifters for quick and effortless shifts
  • Aluminum handlebar, stem and adjustable seatpost supply core-level strength, style and performance
  • Kenda Komodo tires use a non-directional tread design to shed mud without compromising speed
  • ProMax mechanical disc brakes provide low maintenance, all-weather stopping power

ProductShortDescription: If you want baptism by air, here’s your ride. Not only does this bike clear big jumps with ease, its tough, chromoly frame feels nearly weightless when you’re off the ground! Add on 100mm of front suspension to cushion the drops and 3-piece cranks for that sweet barspin.
ProductLongDescription:
• Heavy-duty chromoly frame provides extra strength for jumps at the park
  • RST Space Jump offers 100mm of plush suspension for those hard hits
  • Heat treated, tubular chromoly 3-piece cranks guarantee a stiff and durable ride
  • Conical washers let you covert this single speed ride to an 8/9 speed bike
  • Hayes MX4 mechanical disc brakes deliver low maintenance, all-weather stopping power
  • Kenda K-Rad and Kenda Kiniption tires are designed for aggressive street jumping
  • Sun Ditch Witch rims with Mongoose rear disc hubs are built to withstand those tough landings on the pavement

ProductShortDescription: Ideal for bike paths, country roads and jaunts into town, this easy-rider uses cross/comfort geometry, inside-the-stays disc mounts.
ProductLongDescription:
• 63mm of air sprung, front suspension gives you plush comfort over uneven terrain
  • FSA Alpha Drive triple cranks with SRAM/SR Suntour drivetrain offers tons of gear options for the hills and the flats
  • Mongoose aluminum handlebars, seatpost and stem deliver core-level strength, style and performance
  • Tektro IO mechanical disc brakes deliver rapid and controlled stopping power in any condition
  • Ritchey SpeedMax Delta tires keep you firmly planted on the trail or road
  • Durable Alex rims with Formula disc hubs maintain strength and rigidity no matter what you encounter
  • Ergo Comfort Dual Density grips and Mongoose Performance Hybrid saddle supply extra cushioning

ProductShortDescription: An enthusiastic, road-ready bike inspired and developed by Montague team.
ProductLongDescription:
• Butted 6061 aluminum frame with Reflex Road tuning for a lightweight and resilient ride
  • T:Nine design gives all women riders a customized fit and look
  • Smooth welded, carbon seatstays and fork smooth out the road ahead
  • K2 Bike Fit System stem supplies personalized bar height without the extra weight
  • Shimano 105 20-speed drivetrain with R600 compact cranks offer plenty of easy and efficient gearing options for the climbs
  • Shimano R700 brake/shift levers (Ultegra-level) with reach adjust are mounted on the T:Nine tuned handlebar to accommodate smaller hands for easier stops and gear changes
  • Selle San Marco Women’s Ischia saddle with T:Nine tuned, carbon seatpost adds personalized comfort - a favorite of the Alliance Team
  • FSA Gossamer dual-pivot brakes provide quick and easy stops
  • Crank Brothers Smarty clipless pedals deliver more power in every rotation
  • Continental Ultra Race tires for comfort and exceptional handling, especially on rough or wet road surfaces
  • American Classic Victory wheelset blends together strength, light weight and performance to give you a smooth, responsive ride in race conditions

ProductShortDescription: All for one, never stopping ‘till we’ve won!” - a verse from a favorite UC Davis fight song that’s led by the Aggie Pack, the largest student-run spirit association in the United States.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hi-Ten steel frame is lightweight, strong and resilient
  • Bullhorn handlebars with leather grips keep you riding in comfort and relaxed style
  • Single speed drivetrain is simple and uncomplicated to maintain
  • Dual spring saddle adds comfort to your backside
  • Rubber Block platform pedals make this bike easy to ride
  • Kenda Cruiser tires roll smoothly over flat or rough terrain
  • Rear coaster brake delivers rapid braking power in any condition
  • Fits anyone up to 6’6

ProductShortDescription: Designed for lightning fast transitions and bike splits.
ProductLongDescription:
• Single reverse pull strap (so it doesn't get hung up in the chain when running through the transition area) and dual finger loops allow you to be on your way faster than ever
  • Ventilated upper paired with a super-stiff ventilated sole provides plenty of airflow to keep your feet cool and dry
  • Soft, comfortable neoprene liner

ProductShortDescription: Big heads usually constitute bigger brains. And if there’s any heads out there we need to protect, it most certainly is those!
ProductLongDescription:
• Fusion In-Mold Microshell with a larger design offers protection and durability for whatever the road or trail dishes out
  • 17 vents bring cool air in through the front, allowing it to pass over your head and then flushes warm air out of the rear ports – so YOU stay cool and your HEAD stays cool
  • Snap-In visor protects your eyes from the sun, rain and any other debris that might fly your way
  • ErgoDial fit system provides easy, one-handed adjustment and the Cam-Lock levers deliver a perfect fit

ProductShortDescription: Så hurtigt. Så agile. Så stabil. Så behagelig. Så simpelt.
ProductLongDescription:
• Aluminium hårdhale ramme er letvægts og leverer solid præstation på stien
  • 100mm plys frontophæng giver kontrol og komfort i variabelt terræn
  • Shimano 24-speed drivetrain med 11 / 32T kassette giver dig masser af gearing muligheder at vælge imellem
  • EZ Fire trigger shifters til hurtige og nemme skift
  • Aluminium håndtag, spindel og justerbar sædepost forsyning kerneniveau styrke, stil og ydeevne
  • Kenda Komodo dæk bruger et ikke-retningsmæssigt slidbane design til at udgyde mudder uden at gå på kompromis med hastigheden
  • ProMax mekaniske skivebremser giver lav vedligeholdelse, alt vejrstopkraft

ProductShortDescription: Ideel til cykelstier, landeveje og jager i byen, bruger denne nem-rytter kryds / komfort geometri, inde-the-stays skive monteringer.
ProductLongDescription:
• 63mm luftudstødning, forreste suspension giver dig pæn komfort over ujævnt terræn
  • FSA Alpha Drive triple cranks med SRAM / SR Suntour drivetrain tilbyder tonsvis af gear muligheder for bakkerne og lejlighederne
  • Mongoose aluminium håndtag, sædepind og stamme leverer styrke, stil og ydeevne på kerneniveau
  • Tektro IO mekaniske skivebremser leverer hurtig og kontrolleret stopkraft i enhver tilstand
  • Ritchey SpeedMax Delta dæk holder dig fast plantet på trail eller vej
  • Holdbare Alex-fælge med Formula-skivehubs opretholder styrke og stivhed, uanset hvad du støder på
  • Ergo Comfort Dual Density greb og Mongoose Performance Hybrid sadeltilførsel ekstra polstring

ProductShortDescription: Hvis du vil have dåb med fly, her er din tur. Ikke alene gør denne cykel klart store spring med lethed, den hårde chromoliske ramme føles næsten vægtløs, når du er ude af jorden! Tilføj på 100mm forreste suspension for at dæmpe dråberne og 3-delt vev for den søde spids.
ProductLongDescription:
• Kraftig chromolyramme giver ekstra styrke til spring i parken
  • RST Space Jump tilbyder 100mm plys suspension for de hårde hits
  • Varmebehandlede, rørformede chromoliske 3-delt vev giver en stiv og holdbar kørsel
  • Koniske skiver gør dig skjult for denne single speed ride til en 8/9 speed cykel
  • Hayes MX4 mekaniske skivebremser leverer lav vedligeholdelse, alt vejrstopkraft
  • Kenda K-Rad og Kenda Kiniption dæk er designet til aggressiv street jump
  • Sun Ditch Witch fælge med mongoose bageste skive nav er bygget til at modstå de hårde landinger på fortovet

ProductShortDescription: En entusiastisk, road-ready cykel inspireret og udviklet af Montague team.
ProductLongDescription:
• Butted 6061 aluminiumsramme med Reflex Road tuning til en let og robust tur
  • T: Nine design giver alle kvinder ryttere en tilpasset pasform og udseende
  • Glatte svejsede koldstole og gaffel glider ud af vejen fremad
  • K2 Bike Fit System stamme leverer personlig bar højde uden ekstravægt
  • Shimano 105 20-trins drivkørsel med R600 kompakte kraner tilbyder masser af nemme og effektive gearingsmuligheder til klatringene
  • Shimano R700 bremse- / skiftehåndtag (Ultegra-niveau) med rækkeviddejustering er monteret på T: Nine tunet håndtag til rumme mindre hånd for lettere stop og gearskifte
  • Selle San Marco Kvinder Ischia-sadlen med T: Ni tunet, carbon-sædepost tilføjer personlig komfort - en favorit af Alliance-teamet
  • FSA Gossamer dual-pivot bremser giver hurtig og nem stop
  • Crank Brothers Smarty klemløse pedaler leverer mere strøm i hver rotation
  • Continental Ultra Race dæk til komfort og ekstraordinær håndtering, især på hårde eller våde veje
  • American Classic Victory Hjulsæt combines strength, light weight and performance to give you a smooth and smooth ride.

ProductShortDescription: Denne racer vil få dig til at væve gennem stramme drejninger, klatre op ubarmhjertige bakker, rejse over kuperet terræn, sprængning gennem vanskelige forhold.
ProductLongDescription:
• 7005 rammet aluminiumsramme er let, stærk og stiv
  • Kugleblæst gaffel og sædepost dæmper vibrationer og giver en jævn, stiv ride
  • FSA Gossamer MegaExo kompakte cranks giver dig en slank og kraftfuld pedal slagtilfælde for lejlighederne og klatrerne
  • Shimano 105 drivkørslen kombinerer pålidelig hastighed og høj ydeevne med utrolig kontrol og respons
  • Kulstof / aluminiums sædepude med aluminiumstang og styret garanterer styrke, stil og ydeevne på kerneniveau
  • Kenda K-932 dæk giver fremragende trækkraft og stabilitet uden at gå på kompromis med hastigheden
  • Alex ALX 270 hjulsæt skærer gennem vinden med bladede eger, aero felger og glatte rullende nav
  • Tektro 992AG lineære træbremser leverer perfekt moduleret stopkraft

ProductShortDescription: Alt for en, stopper aldrig 'indtil vi har vundet!' - et vers fra en favorit UC Davis-kampsang, der ledes af Aggie Pack, den største student-run-åndsforening i USA.
ProductLongDescription:
• Hi-Ten stålramme er letvægts, stærk og elastisk
  • Bullhorn håndtag med læderhåndtag holder dig i komfort og afslappet stil
  • Single speed drivetrain er enkel og ukompliceret at vedligeholde
  • Dobbeltfjedersadel tilføjer komfort til din bagside
  • Gummiblocks platformspedaler gør denne cykel let at køre
  • Kenda Cruiser-dæk ruller jævnt over fladt eller ujævnt terræn
  • Bageste coaster brems giver hurtig bremseffekt i enhver tilstand
  • Passer alle op til 6'6

ProductShortDescription: So fast. So agile. So stable. So comfortable. So simple. Just hop on the light and durable chromoly frame, settle your tush into the comfy saddle, place your feet on the pedals and let the single speed drivetrain do all the work for you.
ProductLongDescription:
• Aluminum hård hale frame is lightweight and delivers solid performance on the trail
  • 100mm of plush front suspension adds control and comfort in variable terrain
  • Shimano 24-speed drivetrain with 11/32T cassette gives you plenty of gearing options to choose from
  • EZ Fire trigger shifters for quick and effortless shifts
  • Aluminum handlebar, stem and adjustable seatpost supply core-level strength, style and performance
  • Kenda Komodo tires use a non-directional tread design to shed mud without compromising speed
  • ProMax mechanical disc brakes provide low maintenance, all-weather stopping power

ProductName: The jacket case, three variant groups
The custom bike case, five variant groups
ProductShortDescription: The Attain Race Disc combines all the proven attributes of our popular Attain Race - comfort, performance and agility - with the added stopping power of disc brakes.
ProductLongDescription:
The smooth, light and powerful brake system actually means you can go faster, by braking later into corners. It also adds a reassuring dose of all-weather reliability for race or training rides, allowing you to concentrate on your performance without worrying about wet roads. And, of course, the Attain Race Disc also has the lively handling and balanced geometry that you'd expect from Cube.

Frame: The Attain Race Disc shares its Superlite aluminium frame - built using our Smooth Welding manufacturing process - with its rim brake stablemate, but we've modified it to work brilliantly with discs. The rear end's clean looks are matched by its ability to absorb road shock and vibration without sacrificing transmission effiency.

And the carbon fork - which, like the frame, will accept tyres up to 28mm - also features a specially designed mount for the front disc caliper. A tapered head tube, PressFit bottom bracket and a specially shaped, oversized down tube all help ensure every single pedal stroke counts. And the clean looks afforded by disc brakes have been enhanced by taking the trouble to route cables internally, reducing abrasion and increasing service life at the same time.

ProductName: Cube attain race disk (A lot of features)
ProductShortDescription: The Attain Race Disc combines all the proven attributes of our popular Attain Race - comfort, performance and agility - with the added stopping power of disc brakes. The smooth, light and powerful brake system actually means you can go faster, by braking later into corners. It also adds a reassuring dose of all-weather reliability for race or training rides, allowing you to concentrate on your performance without worrying about wet roads. And, of course, the Attain Race Disc also has the lively handling and balanced geometry that you'd expect from Cube.
ProductLongDescription:
Frame: The Attain Race Disc shares its Superlite aluminium frame - built using our Smooth Welding manufacturing process - with its rim brake stablemate, but we've modified it to work brilliantly with discs. The rear end's clean looks are matched by its ability to absorb road shock and vibration without sacrificing transmission effiency. And the carbon fork - which, like the frame, will accept tyres up to 28mm - also features a specially designed mount for the front disc caliper. A tapered head tube, PressFit bottom bracket and a specially shaped, oversized down tube all help ensure every single pedal stroke counts. And the clean looks afforded by disc brakes have been enhanced by taking the trouble to route cables internally, reducing abrasion and increasing service life at the same time.

Features: That Attain Race Disc features Shimano's versatile, all-round 2x10 Tiagra group, complete with 160mm discs front and rear for smooth, assured stopping in any weather conditions. An 11-34 tooth cassette and compact crank with 50 and 34 tooth chainrings gives a gear range that'll easily tackle both the steepest climbs and the fastest descents. Disc brakes demand special attention to wheels, which is why our engineers selected Fulcrum's Racing 77 wheelset and fitted them with super-grippy Continental Ultra Sport 2 tyres - superb acceleration and stopping, on any road surface.

The Transeo 1.0 has everything you’ve been looking for! It’s lightweight, thanks to the 7005 aluminum frame with hydroformed top tube and cold forged 3D dropouts. It’s fast, due to the 700c wheels that’ll keep you on the go. It’s powerful, because the linear-pull brakes will stop you in your tracks. It’s comfortable, because it boasts an anatomical saddle and soft grips. Each of these features compliments the upright geometry and ergonomics of this fitness machine perfectly.
ProductLongDescription:
• GT 7000 Series butted aluminum frame with Sport Fitness Geometry is built for lightweight speed and durable comfort
  • Suspension fork smoothes out the rough stuff on the road or trail
  • Shimano/SRAM 27-speed drivetrain with RapidFire shifting gives you quick access to plenty of gearing options
  • Selle San Marco Ischia K saddle and dual density grips add comfort over uneven terrain
  • ProMax direct-pull brakes provide excellent stopping power
  • WTB All Terrainasaurus tires are perfect for rough roads and packed trails
  • Double wall Alex rims with Shimano hubs maintain strength and rigidity

ProductShortDescription: Wenn Sie die Taufe in der Luft wünschen, hier ist Ihre Fahrt. Nicht nur, dass dieses Bike große Sprünge mit Leichtigkeit ausradiert, sein harter, chromfarbener Rahmen fühlt sich fast schwerelos an, wenn Sie auf dem Boden sind! Fügen Sie auf 100mm der vorderen Suspendierung hinzu, um die Tropfen und 3-teilige Kurbeln für diese süße Barspin abzufangen.
ProductLongDescription:
• Heavy-Duty Chromoly-Rahmen bietet zusätzliche Stärke für Sprünge im Park
  • RST Space Jump bietet 100mm Plüschfederung für diese harten Schläge
  • Wärmebehandelte, dreiteilige Chromoly-3-teilige Kurbeln garantieren eine steife und langlebige Fahrt
  • Konische Unterlegscheiben lassen Sie diese einzelne Geschwindigkeit Fahrt zu einem 8/9 Fahrrad fahren
  • Die mechanischen Hayes MX4-Scheibenbremsen bieten eine wartungsarme Allwetter-Bremsleistung
  • Kenda K-Rad und Kenda Kinistration Reifen sind für aggressives Street-Jumping ausgelegt
  • Sun Ditch-Witch-Felgen mit Mongoose-Disc-Hinterradnaben sind so konstruiert, dass sie harten Landungen auf dem Asphalt standhalten

ProductShortDescription: Si vous voulez le baptême par avion, voici votre manège. Non seulement cette moto efface-t-elle facilement les grands sauts, mais son cadre robuste et chromoly est presque sans poids lorsque vous quittez le sol! Ajouter 100mm de suspension avant pour amortir les gouttes et les manivelles à 3 pièces pour cette douce barre.
ProductLongDescription:
• Cadre chromoly robuste pour une résistance accrue aux sauts au parc
  • Space Jump offre 100 mm de suspension en peluche pour ces coups durs
  • Les manivelles 3 pièces chromoly traitées thermiquement garantissent une conduite rigide et durable
  • Les rondelles coniques vous permettent de convertir ce vélo à un vélo 8/9 vitesses
  • Les freins à disque mécaniques Hayes MX4 offrent un faible pouvoir d'entretien et une puissance d'arrêt tout temps
  • Les pneus Kenda K-Rad et Kenda Kiniption sont conçus pour les sauts de rue agressifs
